                "text": "A rifti\u2019s unstable shape grants it fluctuating energy attacks and immunities. Each round, to determine which energy applies, roll 1d8: 1\u20132 acid, 3\u20134 electricity, 5\u20136 sonic, 7 cold, 8 fire.",
